               All which tend hereunto at the laste, to witte, that we should humbly submit our selues to the Bondage of the Pope: for this is the pleasaunt bayte whereat Osorius would haue vs fayne to be hooked, this is his whole practise and endeuour. But before hee shall be able to allure vs to that, he must furnishe hys hookes agayne with fresher bayte, somewhat more handsomely couched. For with this touchangle he may fishe a good while, &amp; catch a foole at the last.
