                  e, that as men you may lumper and trippe: Go to then, to what Sanctuary do ye afterwardes fleé for reliefe? Forsooth to a rotten plancke, that may saue a man amyddes the swallowyng gulfe, beyng throwen ouer boorde into the Sea:Of Confession. 
