should make any difference betwixt an vnmaried Priest, &amp; a maried Priest, as to Iudge the one more holy then the other, in respect of his vnmaried lyfe. I will annexe the wordes of the Coūcell: If any man doe take exception betwixt a Maried Priest, at that in respect of his Mariadge, he ought not to minister the Communion, and so sequester him selfe from Communicating with him, let him be accursed.
