ublique and priuate tranquillitie, she retourne agayne to the auncient obedience of the mother Church of Rome, and yeld her humble obeysaunce to the Pope hygh Byshopp thereof as next vnto Christ, and Christ his owne generall Vicar ouer all the face of the earth.
               
